data.description: Beautiful Beatrix located in Avalon in On Top of the World. This home has 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a spacious flex room, and a 2.5 car garage. At the entrance of the home is a spacious flex room, set up as an office, with a ceiling fan and glass French doors with blinds. Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the main area of the home. Across the hall is the 2nd bedroom with carpet, ceiling fan, closet and blinds. The guest bathroom has a single vanity sink with quartz counters, and a tub/shower with tile. The open great room with tray ceiling, fan, and large windows is great for entertaining! The gourmet kitchen features a large island, granite counters, tile backsplash, staggered white cabinets, and stainless steel appliances including the built in oven and microwave, and cooktop with hood. The dining area leads to the screened lanai. The master bedroom has a tray ceiling, carpet, ceiling fan, and large windows to bring in the sunshine! Master bathroom has 2 single vanity sinks with quartz counters, large double door linen cabinet, walk-in shower with tile and niche, and a huge walk-in closet with easy access into the laundry room! The laundry room has built in cabinets with quartz counters, sink, and LG washer/dryer. Enjoy the Florida sunshine in the screened lanai. Backyard is fenced with 4ft vinyl fencing and with a paver patio. Welcome home!
